(157696, 0, 0, 'As do I. Come, Lentios.', 12, 0, 100, 669, 0, 169257, 0, 'Nemea to Player'),
(157696, 1, 0, 'Due to the anima drought, the cloudstriders no longer shed their antlers... you will have to collect them off of their bodies. I implore you to not be wasteful, and to use as many parts of the cloudstriders as you can.', 12, 0, 100, 669, 0, 0, 0, 'Nemea to Player'),
(157696, 2, 0, '$n, you return! Andira seems happy. I think she\'s taken a liking to you!', 12, 0, 100, 669, 0, 0, 0, 'Nemea to Player'),
(157696, 3, 0, 'Larions are social creatures. Andira will not eat without her pride. It is vital that we bring food back to the retreat.', 12, 0, 100, 669, 0, 0, 0, 'Nemea to Player'),
(157696, 4, 0, 'I hope bonding with Andira softened you to my way of life. Larions are more than just companions. Never have I felt a bond with anybody else, kyrian or otherwise, that could be more rewarding than my relationships with my pride.', 12, 0, 100, 669, 0, 0, 0, 'Nemea to Player'),
(157696, 5, 0, 'I knew that you felt the pull of kinship, $n. Andira and the other larions shall be pleased for you to return.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Nemea to Player'),
(157696, 6, 0, 'The pride will be overjoyed to have you, $n. Return soon, there is plenty more bonding to be done.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Nemea to Player'),
